Price Option 2: Awards: The Balnaves family belongs to the first rank of Coonawarra growers, thanks to their immaculate vineyard holdings and viticulture, and the considently outstanding quality of the wines. This takes place on solids in French barriques (31% new), where it is then matured for 11 months.
